quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  7,94,Whenever my sent prophet any obec my afflicted its ludia adversity hardship they implore
  7,95,Potom my zastupid peace prosperity v miesto z ze hardship. Lenze alas they turned heedless said bol our rodicia zazitok hardship prosperity. Consequently my punished them zrazu when they maly expected
  7,96,Had ludia those obec verit turned righteous my lejak them blessings heaven zem. Since they decided disbelieve my punished them co they zarabat
  7,97,Ludia present obec zaruka ze our retribution nie pojdem them night mat rad they spat
  7,98,Ludia dnes obec zaruka ze our retribution nie pojdem them daytime chvila they hraju
  7,99,they berie GOD's plans for granted Ziaden berie GOD's plans for granted losers